short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Chrome Extension for producing study guide based on GradeScope Assignments

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A Plus is a a Chrome extension that collects wrong questions from all graded works on GradeScope for Computer Science/Electrical Engineering students who want to efficiently review past assignments. 
This product allows download for organized wrong problems and provides class performance statistics.
Currently version has only been tested with selected University of Michgian EECS courses. Please let us know if it doesn't work for your educational institution, and we would be happy to make an update for you.
Developed collaboratively by University of Michigan undergraduate students Bo Lu, Nelson Yang, and Chengxi Li.
